Manager Zhang.

869
00:32:10,570 --> 00:32:11,000
Hello, Manager Zhang.

870
00:32:11,000 --> 00:32:11,600
Keep busy.

871
00:32:11,960 --> 00:32:13,050
I specifically came to see

872
00:32:13,050 --> 00:32:14,030
our Ms. Ranran.

873
00:32:14,220 --> 00:32:15,080
Manager Zhang.

874
00:32:15,810 --> 00:32:18,230
That scene just now was fantastic.

875
00:32:18,610 --> 00:32:19,870
I specifically got you

876
00:32:19,980 --> 00:32:21,640
some imported mineral water.

877
00:32:21,750 --> 00:32:22,400
I prepared

878
00:32:22,420 --> 00:32:23,590
a private lounge for you.

879
00:32:23,590 --> 00:32:24,800
The AC is already on.

880
00:32:24,850 --> 00:32:26,270
Once you're done with makeup,

881
00:32:26,270 --> 00:32:27,290
you can go back to the lounge

882
00:32:27,290 --> 00:32:28,070
and comfortably

883
00:32:28,070 --> 00:32:29,730
read your script and make art.

884
00:32:29,940 --> 00:32:30,670
Sounds good?

885
00:32:32,570 --> 00:32:33,390
Mr. Xie,

886
00:32:33,940 --> 00:32:35,940
do a good job on our Ranran's makeup.

887
00:32:36,050 --> 00:32:36,650
Of course.

888
00:32:36,900 --> 00:32:39,100
She looks like a born leading lady.

889
00:32:39,420 --> 00:32:39,880
Indeed.

890
00:32:40,290 --> 00:32:42,060
I'll let you get back to work.

891
00:32:42,330 --> 00:32:43,500
Let me know if you need anything.

892
00:32:43,500 --> 00:32:43,880
Okay?

893
00:32:43,900 --> 00:32:44,930
-Okay.
-Go ahead.

894
00:32:45,550 --> 00:32:49,110
[Dressing Room]

895
00:32:45,750 --> 00:32:46,480
Do a good job.

896
00:32:47,140 --> 00:32:47,810
Take care.

897
00:32:48,050 --> 00:32:48,550
Bye.

898
00:32:55,920 --> 00:32:57,520
Thank you for your hard work.

899
00:32:57,680 --> 00:32:58,940
Here, have some water.

900
00:32:59,960 --> 00:33:01,900
-Ms. Wang, have some water.
-Thank you.

901
00:33:01,900 --> 00:33:03,120
I'm really sorry.

902
00:33:03,180 --> 00:33:05,580
The director might be in a hurry

903
00:33:06,140 --> 00:33:07,830
with the costume and set change.

904
00:33:07,830 --> 00:33:08,480
Thank you.

905
00:33:08,880 --> 00:33:10,720
We couldn't afford

906
00:33:10,770 --> 00:33:12,570
such expensive water on our own.

907
00:33:12,590 --> 00:33:14,450
We don't get such good treatment.

908
00:33:23,770 --> 00:33:24,610
It's fine.

909
00:33:24,670 --> 00:33:26,800
Your acting just now was really great.

910
00:33:27,010 --> 00:33:28,610
Don't take it to heart, okay?

911
00:33:29,010 --> 00:33:30,410
Let's start your makeup.

912
00:33:39,620 --> 00:33:40,660
[Spring is not Far Away]

913
00:34:10,880 --> 00:34:11,610
Ranran,

914
00:34:12,630 --> 00:34:13,889
I told you to come over,

915
00:34:14,010 --> 00:34:15,060
but you didn't.

916
00:34:15,110 --> 00:34:16,770
Why are you hiding here alone?

917
00:34:18,460 --> 00:34:19,050
All the

918
00:34:19,150 --> 00:34:20,550
famous producers and directors

919
00:34:20,550 --> 00:34:21,590
are in that room.

920
00:34:21,710 --> 00:34:23,760
Let me tell you the good news.

921
00:34:24,550 --> 00:34:27,080
Everyone's asking about your availability.

922
00:34:27,760 --> 00:34:29,000
One thing's for sure:

923
00:34:31,090 --> 00:34:31,949
you've made it.

924
00:34:38,710 --> 00:34:39,440
Mr. Chu,

925
00:34:40,780 --> 00:34:41,920
they didn't shoot

926
00:34:42,260 --> 00:34:44,010
much of my part in that project.

927
00:34:46,820 --> 00:34:48,150
If it were someone else,

928
00:34:52,130 --> 00:34:53,840
what would I pay?

929
00:34:55,820 --> 00:34:56,710
What's wrong,

930
00:34:57,620 --> 00:34:58,290
Ranran?

931
00:34:59,800 --> 00:35:00,660
What happened?

932
00:35:00,960 --> 00:35:02,960
Why are you suddenly asking me this?

933
00:35:04,190 --> 00:35:05,130
All along,

934
00:35:05,340 --> 00:35:06,650
relying on my own ability to act

935
00:35:06,650 --> 00:35:08,030
has been my greatest dream

936
00:35:08,030 --> 00:35:09,450
and the happiest thing.

937
00:35:09,960 --> 00:35:10,340
Then,

938
00:35:10,690 --> 00:35:12,090
your dream has come true.

939
00:35:12,710 --> 00:35:14,420
You should be happy now.

940
00:35:16,610 --> 00:35:17,530
I am not happy.

941
00:35:35,280 --> 00:35:36,650
You can walk away from the role,

942
00:35:36,650 --> 00:35:38,510
but you will have to pay the price.

943
00:35:40,150 --> 00:35:41,280
You'll have to cover

944
00:35:41,510 --> 00:35:43,710
all the upfront costs:

945
00:35:45,050 --> 00:35:45,800
script development,

946
00:35:45,800 --> 00:35:47,130
costume, makeup, set design,

947
00:35:47,130 --> 00:35:47,990
camera, sound,

948
00:35:48,530 --> 00:35:49,980
art direction—

949
00:35:50,690 --> 00:35:51,940
every department.

950
00:35:55,630 --> 00:35:57,010
Let me put it this way.

951
00:35:57,480 --> 00:36:00,110
You're basically ruined in this industry.

952
00:36:04,980 --> 00:36:05,380
Stop.

953
00:36:06,320 --> 00:36:07,690
You've had enough.

954
00:36:08,130 --> 00:36:08,990
Stop drinking.

955
00:36:12,860 --> 00:36:13,540
Ranran,

956
00:36:14,230 --> 00:36:15,560
the first time I saw you,

957
00:36:16,780 --> 00:36:17,670
I fell for you.

958
00:36:21,780 --> 00:36:22,400
Look,

959
00:36:24,070 --> 00:36:25,420
so many actresses

960
00:36:26,980 --> 00:36:28,440
want to become stars.

961
00:36:29,280 --> 00:36:30,190
But how could they get

962
00:36:30,190 --> 00:36:32,120
such a good opportunity as you did?

963
00:36:32,840 --> 00:36:35,900
I used all my resources
to make you famous,

964
00:36:36,780 --> 00:36:38,180
but you don't cherish it.

965
00:36:39,280 --> 00:36:40,010
I don't want to see

966
00:36:40,010 --> 00:36:41,130
your future

967
00:36:42,840 --> 00:36:44,040
become so miserable.

968
00:36:45,550 --> 00:36:46,510
The reason I'm saying this

969
00:36:46,510 --> 00:36:47,250
is to tell you

970
00:36:47,300 --> 00:36:48,560
that I understand you.

971
00:36:49,400 --> 00:36:50,530
Everyone is rushing

972
00:36:50,550 --> 00:36:51,460
to get into this industry

973
00:36:51,460 --> 00:36:52,820
because it's glamorous.

974
00:36:52,820 --> 00:36:53,690
But you

975
00:36:55,610 --> 00:36:57,050
don't think it's that glamorous.

976
00:36:57,050 --> 00:36:57,870
Tell me, am I

977
00:36:58,900 --> 00:36:59,530
right?

978
00:37:01,070 --> 00:37:03,050
Of course, if you really don't
want to act anymore,

979
00:37:03,050 --> 00:37:04,210
I can help you.

980
00:37:15,670 --> 00:37:16,360
Mr. Chu,

981
00:37:17,320 --> 00:37:18,130
rest assured.

982
00:37:18,760 --> 00:37:20,170
I will definitely

983
00:37:20,170 --> 00:37:21,700
finish this show properly.

984
00:37:22,860 --> 00:37:23,380
Don't.

985
00:37:23,860 --> 00:37:24,260
Don't.

986
00:37:28,780 --> 00:37:29,260
Ranran,

987
00:37:34,710 --> 00:37:35,310
remember:

988
00:37:36,880 --> 00:37:38,540
don't push yourself too hard.

989
00:37:38,960 --> 00:37:39,860
I'm here.

990
00:37:40,360 --> 00:37:42,360
I won't let anyone hurt you.

991
00:37:44,860 --> 00:37:45,720
We'll walk away

992
00:37:46,650 --> 00:37:47,710
from this project.

993
00:37:48,920 --> 00:37:51,030
I'll handle all the compensation.

994
00:37:52,660 --> 00:37:54,460
You know I like you.

995
00:38:56,770 --> 00:38:58,740
I don't need anything you give me.

996
00:38:59,440 --> 00:39:00,980
Don't contact me again.

997
00:39:06,490 --> 00:39:10,860
[I Am a Stranger]

998
00:39:15,290 --> 00:39:15,830
[Golden Garden at Sunset]

999
00:39:18,390 --> 00:39:21,370
[Golden Garden at Sunset]

1000
00:39:28,510 --> 00:39:29,280
You know,

1001
00:39:29,610 --> 00:39:30,530
over all these years,

1002
00:39:30,530 --> 00:39:32,270
I've spent so much

1003
00:39:32,320 --> 00:39:34,320
just hiring acting coaches for you.

1004
00:39:34,740 --> 00:39:36,000
You are a money-loser.

1005
00:39:38,400 --> 00:39:39,100
Mom,

1006
00:39:39,920 --> 00:39:42,220
did you borrow money from Mr. Chu?

1007
00:39:41,660 --> 00:39:42,470
[Love Debt]

1008
00:39:43,110 --> 00:39:46,440
[I Am a Stranger]

1009
00:39:47,030 --> 00:39:48,230
Of everyone I've met,

1010
00:39:49,010 --> 00:39:50,150
you set

1011
00:39:51,570 --> 00:39:52,830
the highest standard.

1012
00:39:52,960 --> 00:39:54,470
Big star Shen,

1013
00:39:54,500 --> 00:39:56,380
your success is just around the corner.

1014
00:39:56,380 --> 00:39:57,590
My dream of art

1015
00:39:57,690 --> 00:40:00,410
will surely bloom beautifully

1016
00:40:00,500 --> 00:40:02,010
and fragrantly.

1017
00:40:03,810 --> 00:40:06,770
[Name: Shen Ranran] [Film Performance Art]

1018
00:40:49,800 --> 00:40:50,660
Director Weng,

1019
00:40:50,690 --> 00:40:51,610
I called Xu Shengli for you.

1020
00:40:51,610 --> 00:40:52,740
He'll be right here.

1021
00:40:53,070 --> 00:40:54,500
I've seen your plays.

1022
00:40:54,650 --> 00:40:55,710
I really like them.

1023
00:40:56,230 --> 00:40:57,440
I am Little Northeasterner.

1024
00:40:57,440 --> 00:40:59,280
I'm the boss of Seasons Change Hostel.

1025
00:40:59,280 --> 00:41:00,340
Come to our place when you have time.

1026
00:41:00,340 --> 00:41:01,440
I'll treat you to a meal.

1027
00:41:01,440 --> 00:41:02,900
Who needs you to treat him?

1028
00:41:03,170 --> 00:41:04,030
Director Weng,

1029
00:41:04,380 --> 00:41:04,980
has the start date for our play

1030
00:41:04,980 --> 00:41:06,140
been decided yet?

1031
00:41:06,630 --> 00:41:07,320
Xu,

1032
00:41:09,980 --> 00:41:12,230
Oh no. I'm done.

1033
00:41:13,210 --> 00:41:14,520
Mr. Sui

1034
00:41:14,940 --> 00:41:16,500
ran away with money.

1035
00:41:20,460 --> 00:41:24,010
["The Late Love"
Filming Team–Producer's Office]

1036
00:41:22,340 --> 00:41:22,900
Xu,

1037
00:41:23,650 --> 00:41:25,280
how is it? Did you find him?

1038
00:41:25,940 --> 00:41:27,130
His family went abroad

1039
00:41:27,130 --> 00:41:28,200
a few months ago.

1040
00:41:28,690 --> 00:41:29,820
The police also said

1041
00:41:29,900 --> 00:41:30,920
he used our project

1042
00:41:30,920 --> 00:41:32,180
to scam many investors

1043
00:41:32,210 --> 00:41:33,340
out of a lot of money.

1044
00:41:33,410 --> 00:41:37,470
[The Late Love Filming Team]

1045
00:41:35,280 --> 00:41:36,090
So, Director,

1046
00:41:36,320 --> 00:41:37,360
are we really not

1047
00:41:37,530 --> 00:41:39,060
making this movie anymore?

1048
00:41:39,860 --> 00:41:40,920
Xu,

1049
00:41:42,170 --> 00:41:43,300
when making a movie,

1050
00:41:44,400 --> 00:41:45,820
anything can happen.

1051
00:41:46,530 --> 00:41:47,010
Wait,

1052
00:41:47,830 --> 00:41:48,860
we've gone through

1053
00:41:48,860 --> 00:41:50,100
so much trouble.

1054
00:41:50,210 --> 00:41:51,210
We bet

1055
00:41:51,210 --> 00:41:52,210
our lives on this.

1056
00:41:52,320 --> 00:41:53,860
Aren't we sincere enough?

1057
00:41:54,960 --> 00:41:55,490
Shengli,

1058
00:42:00,500 --> 00:42:02,060
no matter how well you plan,

1059
00:42:02,760 --> 00:42:04,490
you can't predict everything.

1060
00:42:05,510 --> 00:42:06,110
By the way,

1061
00:42:06,550 --> 00:42:07,160
you

1062
00:42:07,420 --> 00:42:08,210
better go to the bank

1063
00:42:08,210 --> 00:42:09,630
and check how

1064
00:42:09,630 --> 00:42:10,460
your loan contract was signed.

1065
00:42:10,460 --> 00:42:11,360
Why should I care about

1066
00:42:11,360 --> 00:42:12,510
my contract?

1067
00:42:12,720 --> 00:42:14,320
What about our crew?

1068
00:42:17,110 --> 00:42:19,900
Well, the studio's money

1069
00:42:20,230 --> 00:42:21,210
was supposed to be given

1070
00:42:21,210 --> 00:42:23,070
when you were halfway through.

1071
00:42:23,090 --> 00:42:23,920
So at least

1072
00:42:24,000 --> 00:42:25,330
we don't owe the studio.

1073
00:42:25,650 --> 00:42:28,170
We borrowed 500,000 yuan from the bank.

1074
00:42:29,400 --> 00:42:30,760
Before shooting,

1075
00:42:31,880 --> 00:42:33,570
we spent

1076
00:42:33,570 --> 00:42:34,720
about 100,000 yuan,

1077
00:42:34,920 --> 00:42:35,760
which came from

1078
00:42:35,760 --> 00:42:36,940
our loan.

1079
00:42:37,280 --> 00:42:38,010
The rest

1080
00:42:38,530 --> 00:42:39,420
was taken away

1081
00:42:39,420 --> 00:42:40,170
by Mr. Sui.

1082
00:42:40,170 --> 00:42:41,130
Then there's the

1083
00:42:41,130 --> 00:42:42,390
actors' upfront fees,

1084
00:42:43,260 --> 00:42:45,890
set construction, and staff salaries—

1085
00:42:46,010 --> 00:42:47,570
we'll have the Manager tally that up.

1086
00:42:47,570 --> 00:42:48,480
Like I said,

1087
00:42:49,280 --> 00:42:50,860
every play has its own fate.

1088
00:42:51,560 --> 00:42:56,230
[The Late Love Filming Team]

1089
00:42:52,300 --> 00:42:54,330
No matter how unacceptable it is,

1090
00:42:55,010 --> 00:42:55,980
you have to accept it.
